---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroImage from '../components/HeroImage.astro';
import TrustBar from '../components/TrustBar.astro';
import Reviews from '../components/Reviews.astro';
import CTABlock from '../components/CTABlock.astro';
import { BUSINESS, YEARS_IN_BUSINESS } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Tom Falk Plumbing and Heating in Millersville PA"
  description="A family-owned plumbing and HVAC shop in Millersville PA, serving Lancaster County since 1961, founded by Jim and Edna Falk. Meet the family shop."
  canonicalPath="/about"
  quoteHref="/contact#quote"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h1>A family shop in Millersville since {BUSINESS.foundingYear}</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        {BUSINESS.founders} started Tom Falk Plumbing &amp; Heating in {BUSINESS.foundingYear}.
        {YEARS_IN_BUSINESS} years later it's still a family business, still in
        {BUSINESS.addressLocality}, still answering to its own name in this community.
      </p>
      <HeroImage name="IMG_20260713_132310.jpg"
                 alt="Two branded Tom Falk service vans and an American flag beside a newly installed air-conditioning condenser." eager />
      <div style="margin-top:1.25rem"><TrustBar /></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Same family, same standards</h2>
      <p>
        A lot of our customers have known us as their plumber for decades. Now we bring
        that same approach to full heating and cooling. When you call, you get a local
        team — {BUSINESS.credentials.toLowerCase()} — not a call center and not a
        rotating crew of subcontractors. The people who show up are the people who answer
        to the name on the van.
      </p>

      <h2>Not a private-equity rollup</h2>
      <p>
        A lot of the names advertising around Lancaster County are backed by out-of-town
        investors now. We're not one of them. We're the shop that's been down the street
        since {BUSINESS.foundingYear}, and that's the whole difference: we live here, we
        answer for our own work, and we'll be here if you ever need us again.
      </p>

      <h2>How we do the work</h2>
      <p>
        We size systems with a real load calculation instead of guessing. We're an
        authorized dealer for Amana and Rheem. We back our installs with a 1-year labor
        guarantee, extendable up to 10 years, plus manufacturer warranties, and we offer
        financing through Synchrony. And we'll always tell you straight whether it's time
        to replace something or whether it has life left — because that's how you keep a
        customer for 65 years.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Reviews limit={6} />
  <CTABlock heading="Want that kind of shop on your side?" />
</BaseLayout>
